The paper focuses on video classification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method involves attention mechanisms (cs.MM) and adversarial learning (cs.LG), which are commonly used in deep learning research. The paper also mentions the use of semantic guidance (cs.AI) and multi-scale features (cs.IR) to improve classification performance.
